Class EvaluationEnvironment

Represents an environment encapsulating common entities used during command evaluation.

public sealed class EvaluationEnvironment
Remarks

This class provides quick access to frequently needed Discord entities such as the message, channel, guild, user, and client related to the current command context. It's designed to simplify command handling by centralizing access to these entities.
